; Coverage for value.cc
; When --exchange specifies source:target and the source commodity is
; not found, sources[index] is nullptr. For a BALANCE value this
; exercises the nullptr source branch where should_convert falls through
; to the non-source path

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $100.00
    Expenses:Drink   50 EUR
    Assets:Cash

P 2024/01/01 $ 0.90 EUR

test bal --exchange FAKE:EUR
         -140.00 EUR  Assets:Cash
          140.00 EUR  Expenses
           50.00 EUR    Drink
           90.00 EUR    Food
--------------------
                   0
end test
